[Guest]: And in 2016, it was around 500 billion.

00:28:22.040 --> 00:28:25.400
[Guest]: So basically, within a period of one year, it went up by around 10%.

00:28:25.400 --> 00:28:26.960
[Guest]: Now, what does that mean?

